snippet.title: AMID THE LINES Gameplay (PC Game)
snippet.description:
Amid the lines is A beat’em up with amazing fighting mechanics ,and an interesting storyline that will leave you wanting more. join detective Northwood’s journey and fight his fight.
Support the developer by purchasing the game on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1611110/AMID_THE_LINES/
